Tidak akan lama.

504
00:35:46.290 --> 00:35:46.770
Ini.

505
00:35:47.120 --> 00:35:47.970
Terima kasih.

506
00:35:49.370 --> 00:35:51.240
Kakak He Ming, kau sangat baik.

507
00:35:55.720 --> 00:35:56.810
Sayang sekali.

508
00:35:57.930 --> 00:35:59.680
Kau orang Negara Jin Po.

