00:36:54.240 --> 00:36:56.370
Cantik sekali! Lihatlah ke sana.

524
00:36:57.770 --> 00:36:58.490
Hati-hati.

525
00:37:04.640 --> 00:37:06.770
Terima kasih, Kakak He Ming.

526
00:37:17.520 --> 00:37:20.520
Ayahku berkata
setelah musim dingin berakhir,

527
00:37:21.200 --> 00:37:22.930
perang akan kembali dimulai.

528
00:37:29.640 --> 00:37:30.680
Kakak He Ming,

529
00:37:31.970 --> 00:37:33.160
jika kami kalah,

